text: Marrickville is a suburb in the Inner West of Sydney,Australian Suburb Guide: Sydney Inner West Retrieved 8 August 2013. in the state of New South Wales, Australia. Marrickville is south-west of the Sydney central business district and is the largest suburb in the Inner West Council local government area. In 2025, the Metro North West and Bankstown Line will extend to Bankstown via Marrickville. ==References== Category:Suburbs of Sydney
title: Marrickville, New South Wales
